@startuml Protection Proxy Core Components

interface Resource {
    + access(): void
}

class RealResource implements Resource {
    + access(): void
}

class ProtectionProxy implements Resource {
    - realResource: RealResource
    - userPermissions: String
    + ProtectionProxy(resource: RealResource, permissions: String)
    + access(): void
    - checkAuthorization(): boolean
}

note right: Controls access based on permissions
note right: Security validation before access

ProtectionProxy *-- RealResource
Client ..> ProtectionProxy : uses

@enduml
